text: G Men is a 1935 American crime drama movie directed by William Keighley and starring James Cagney, Margaret Lindsay, Ann Dvorak, Robert Armstrong, Barton MacLane, Lloyd Nolan, William Harrigan, Russell Hopton, Edward Pawley. It was distributed by Warner Bros. and was nominated for an Academy Award in 1936. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1935 drama movies Category:1930s American crime drama movies Category:Warner Bros. movies Category:Movies directed by William Keighley
